What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Spectrophotometric Plate Reader Market?

Analysis and Size

The global spectrophotometric plate reader market has grown in recent years as research institutes and biotech businesses have focused more on the healthcare industry. Furthermore, technological improvements have made it feasible to provide more trustworthy data in comparison to traditional measurements. Consequently, the presence of various growth determinants will propel the growth forward over the forecasted period.

Global Spectrophotometric Plate Reader Market was valued at USD 222.94 million in 2021 and is expected to reach USD 381.68 million by 2029, registering a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period of 2022-2029. The "multi-mode" accounts for the largest mode segment in the spectrophotometric plate reader market within the forecasted period due to their ability to detect two or more applications. The market report curated by the Data Bridge Market Research team includes in-depth expert analysis, patient epidemiology, pipeline analysis, pricing analysis, and regulatory framework.

